parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The illumination of the airbag warning light can indicate a potential malfunction of the airbag system, which can lead to a failure to deploy in the event of an accident, potentially causing serious injury or death.
symptoms: The airbag warning light remains illuminated on the dashboard
the airbag system fails to pass state inspection
the airbag system is inoperable.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the airbag system can lead to a failure to deploy in the event of an accident, potentially causing serious injury or death.
symptoms: The airbag is protruding from the dashboard
the airbag system is inoperable
the airbag warning light remains illuminated on the dashboard.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The delay or unavailability of recall repairs can leave vehicles with potentially life-threatening defects on the road, putting drivers and passengers at risk.
symptoms: The manufacturer is unable to provide the necessary parts for recall repairs
the dealership is unable to perform the recall repairs due to part unavailability
the manufacturer exceeds a reasonable amount of time for the recall repair.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The unintended gear shifts can cause the vehicle to suddenly lose power, leading to a loss of control, increased stopping distance, and potential accidents.
symptoms: The vehicle suddenly shifts into 3rd gear at high speeds
gets stuck in 3rd gear
warning message "Transmission Fault; Limited Gears" appears
the vehicle's speed drastically reduces
the vehicle will not shift into another gear
the problem resets when the engine is turned off and back on
but reoccurs with greater frequency as the vehicle warms up.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The sudden failure of the brakes can cause the vehicle to lose control, leading to accidents or near-misses, which can result in injuries or fatalities.
symptoms: The brake pedal travels to the floorboard
the brake warning light illuminates
the vehicle stalls or hesitates
the tire pressure light stays on
the vehicle jumps to the side when hitting a bump.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Oil leaking into the valves can cause engine hesitation, stalling, and difficulty starting, which can lead to accidents or leave the driver stranded.
symptoms: The vehicle hesitates or stalls
the engine cuts off
oil leaking into the valves.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The illumination of the suspension low warning light can indicate a problem with the vehicle's suspension, which can affect its handling and stability, leading to accidents or loss of control.
symptoms: The suspension low warning light illuminates
the vehicle stalls or hesitates.
